## 5.2 Impact of FGSM Adversarial Attacks

To evaluate model vulnerability, FGSM adversarial attacks were performed using multiple perturbation strengths.

The classification accuracy of the baseline CNN under adversarial conditions is shown below.

| Epsilon | Accuracy (%) |
| ------- | ------------ |
| 0.01    | 23.13        |
| 0.03    | 7.34         |
| 0.05    | 3.35         |
| 0.10    | 1.04         |

The results indicate a significant degradation in classification performance as the perturbation strength increased. Even a relatively small perturbation value of 0.03 reduced model accuracy from 72.54% to 7.34%, demonstrating the vulnerability of deep learning models to adversarial manipulation.

